      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-red-100 text-red-700 dark:bg-red-900/40 dark:text-red-300 text-xs font-semibold">New</span>
          <span>Two papers accepted to the <strong>11th Indian Control Conference (ICC), Bangalore, 2025</strong>.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 dark:bg-blue-900/40 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-semibold">2025</span>
          <span>Starting M.A.Sc at <strong>University of British Columbia</strong> (Sep 2025), advised by Prof. Cyrus Neary.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-100 text-green-700 dark:bg-green-900/40 dark:text-green-300 text-xs font-semibold">2024</span>
          <span>Paper on congestion-aware path planning published in <strong>Industry 4.0 and Advanced Manufacturing</strong>, Springer.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-green-100 text-green-700 dark:bg-green-900/40 dark:text-green-300 text-xs font-semibold">2024</span>
          <span>Joined <strong>IIT Madras</strong> as a Project Associate working on pursuit-evasion UAVs with Deep RL.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 dark:bg-purple-900/40 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-semibold">2024</span>
          <span>Graduated B.E. Mechanical Engineering from TCE, Madurai — <strong>Department Best Outgoing Student</strong>.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 dark:bg-amber-900/40 dark:text-amber-300 text-xs font-semibold">2024</span>
          <span>U.K. Design Patent filed: <strong>"Robotic Duct Vacuum Cleaner"</strong> (No. 6339408).</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 dark:bg-cyan-900/40 dark:text-cyan-300 text-xs font-semibold">2023</span>
          <span>Ranked <strong>Top 6</strong> in the DePondFi '23 Challenge at NCVPRIPG-2023.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
          <span class="shrink-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 dark:bg-cyan-900/40 dark:text-cyan-300 text-xs font-semibold">2022</span>
          <span>Paper on thermal fire detection accepted at <strong>IC3I 2022</strong>.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-12 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-t from-white dark:from-neutral-950 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

