  <section class="relative z-20 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-7 xl:px-0">
    <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Projects and Competitions</h2>
    <p class="mb-8 text-sm italic text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Below are some of the projects I had fun working on, click the title for details.</p>

<!-- Project: Robotic Manipulation -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/manipulator.gif" alt="Robotic Manipulation using Continuous Deep RL" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://github.com/Dilli-Bhaskar/Robotic-Manipulation-using-Continuous-Deep-RL.git" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        Robotic Manipulation using Continuous Deep RL
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Developed a DRL pipeline to train a 7-DOF robotic arm in the PandaReach-v3 environment using panda-gym. Implemented SAC, NAF, and TD3 with Hindsight Experience Replay to address sparse reward challenges. Evaluated across 3 random seeds achieving a reward of ~-1.768.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: PondFishDet -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/pond.gif" alt="PondFishDet" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://github.com/Dilli-Bhaskar/PondFishDet/tree/main" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        PondFishDet
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Developed CLAHE-YOLOv8 and MSR-YOLOv8 pipelines to improve underwater fish detection under challenging lighting conditions. Ranked Top 6 in the DePondFi ’23 Challenge at NCVPRIPG-2023.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: Street Litter Detection -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/litter.gif" alt="Street Litter Detection" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://github.com/Dilli-Bhaskar/YoloV5_GarbageLitterDetection" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        Street Litter Detection
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Developed a YOLOv5-based model for real-time street litter detection. Trained on PennFudan and TACO datasets achieving an F1 score of 89%. Deployed on CCTV streams for automated monitoring.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: Miniaturized Aircraft -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/aero.gif" alt="Miniaturized Aircraft" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://grabcad.com/dilli.bhaskar-1" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        Design and Fabrication of Miniaturized Aircraft
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Designed and fabricated a rubber-band powered aircraft using lightweight balsa wood and paper structures. Implemented a 20° wing dihedral for flight stability and achieved a flight time of 2 minutes 10 seconds.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: AI Waste Recycling -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/sih.jpg" alt="AI Waste Recycling System" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/10lhWCpZqXJlVEUOKb9OSC5g_wKTLqBl/edit" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        AI-assisted Waste Recycling System
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Smart India Hackathon 2022 winning project. Developed deep learning models to detect roadside waste, classify it into seven recycling categories, and further categorize plastic waste into five shape-based sub-classes.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: IoT Shaker Machine -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/iot.gif" alt="IoT Shaker Machine" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://youtu.be/J2svYU1bzYQ" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        IoT Integration on Shaker Machine
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Developed a low-cost non-contact AC sensor to monitor operational status of components in a shaker machine at the Product Reliability Lab. Data was streamed to Arduino IoT Cloud and Google Drive for long-term monitoring.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: Cycling Helmet CFD -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/cfd.jpg" alt="Helmet CFD Study" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vXyGCEbE6CvqFMZQBBdqHiV0b4k8yWSz/view" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        Aerodynamic Drag Study of Time-Trial Cycling Helmets
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Performed CFD analysis of cycling helmets with tail flap angles of 0°, 3°, and 9° using ANSYS Fluent. Results indicated that tail angles between 6°–9° significantly reduce drag coefficient.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Project: Marine Diesel Piston -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-10 md:flex-row group">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-48 h-32 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800">
    <img src="/assets/images/projects/fea.gif" alt="Marine Diesel Engine Piston" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug dark:text-neutral-100">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rWP8J2dNhh9B4wp1sm_YIqqBlH0uXJqx/view" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
        Design Analysis of Detroit 8V-71 Marine Diesel Engine Piston
      </a>
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      Redesigned piston head profiles for the Detroit 8V-71 marine diesel engine and performed static stress analysis using ANSYS Workbench. The concave head profile demonstrated lower stress and deformation compared to flat and dome designs.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
  </section>

